name: Chinese Lingerie Fusion Design
description:
If you'd like to support me and do more:
https://ko-fi.com/edgonkofi

If you're looking for a >>LoRA Making Tutorial<<

Chinese Lingerie Fusion Design

Originally this work was inspired by Dudou (肚兜) but this LoRA DOES NOT generate Dudou. It can but it's mainly a FUSION design.

FUSION design means that the original design is fused with other concepts. Therefore this is 肚兜 inspired but not traditional 肚兜.

Since 肚兜 was my inspiration, I put "dudou" as trigger word.

Get into the world of Chinese-inspired lingerie and have fun!
